    <h1>Fondant Potatoes</h1>
    <img src="../images/fpotatoes.jpg" alt "Picture of delicious bunch of potatoes">
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
        <ul>3 large whole russet potatoes</ul>
        <ul>2 TBSP high-heat-resistant vegetable oil</ul>
        <ul>salt and ground black pepper to taste</ul>
        <ul>3 TBSP butter</ul>
        <ul>4 sprigs thyme, plus more for garnish</ul>
        <ul>1/2 cup chicken broth, or more as needed</ul>

